Class AbstractControlNodeInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.jcore.controlnodes.AbstractControlNodeInstance
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractEvent, ActivityInstance, EndEvent, GatewayInstance

    public abstract class AbstractControlNodeInstance
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the abstract control node. Each control node has a state, an incoming and outgoing behavior.
